WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.520
My grandmother gave me this marriage advice

00:00:02.521 --> 00:00:05.201
which I still think about to this day.

00:00:05.202 --> 00:00:07.258
She said, find someone who

00:00:07.259 --> 00:00:10.381
 you want to annoy for the rest of your life

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.100
and you'll always be happy.
